    • Uses of TypeDispatcher in org.lfj.lang.util

      Subclasses of TypeDispatcher in org.lfj.lang.util 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  ManualTypeDispatcher
      This is a manual type dispatcher which allows you to dispatch types based upon a set of declared specs.
      class  ReflectiveTypeDispatcher
      This dispatches member specs based upon reflection upon a given class which has already been loaded.
      Constructors in org.lfj.lang.util with parameters of type TypeDispatcher 
      Constructor Description
      ManualTypeDispatcher​(MemberSpec[] specs, TypeDispatcher fallbackDispatcher)
      Construct a manual type dispatcher from an array of declared specs and its fallback dispatcher to be used when there is no name matching specs among the declared specs.
